<Link id="l01545" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1545"><Highlight kind="comment">/// A forward-reference to a template argument that was not known at the point</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01547" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1547"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01548" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1548"><Highlight kind="comment">/// This is created when demangling the name of a specialization of a</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01549" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1549"><Highlight kind="comment">/// conversion function template:</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01550" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1550"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01551" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1551"><Highlight kind="comment">/// \\code</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01552" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1552"><Highlight kind="comment">/// struct A &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01553" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1553"><Highlight kind="comment">///   template&lt;typename T&gt; operator T&#42;();</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01554" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1554"><Highlight kind="comment">/// &#125;;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01555" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1555"><Highlight kind="comment">/// \\endcode</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01556" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1556"><Highlight kind="comment">///</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01557" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1557"><Highlight kind="comment">/// When demangling a specialization of the conversion function template, we</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01558" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1558"><Highlight kind="comment">/// encounter the name of the template (including the \\c T) before we reach</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01559" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1559"><Highlight kind="comment">/// the template argument list, so we cannot substitute the parameter name</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01560" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1560"><Highlight kind="comment">/// for the corresponding argument while parsing. Instead, we create a</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01561" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1561"><Highlight kind="comment">/// \\c ForwardTemplateReference node that is resolved after we parse the</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01562" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1562"><Highlight kind="comment">/// template arguments.</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01563" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1563" lineLink="/docs/api/structs/forwardtemplatereference"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight><Highlight kind="keyword">struct </Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"><a href="/docs/api/structs/forwardtemplatereference/#ac45f331214a30b5feacb4e9cbaffd44c">ForwardTemplateReference</a> : <a href="/docs/api/classes/node/#a7a56ed6baec69c476df398caa5c9aef5">Node</a> &#123;</Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01564" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1564" lineLink="/docs/api/structs/forwardtemplatereference/#a4baab51d7fb8c88ca6bf6bf4c87be0d3"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="keywordtype">size&#95;t</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"> <a href="/docs/api/structs/forwardtemplatereference/#a4baab51d7fb8c88ca6bf6bf4c87be0d3">Index</a>;</Highlight></CodeLine>

<Link id="l01566" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1566"><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
<Link id="l01567" /><CodeLine lineNumber="1567"><Highlight kind="normal">  </Highlight><Highlight kind="comment">// If we&#39;re currently printing this node. It is possible (though invalid) for</Highlight><Highlight kind="normal"></Highlight></CodeLine>
